{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-008__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-008", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·008.1", "text_original": "我出我車，于彼牧矣。自天子所，謂我來矣。\n召彼僕夫，謂之載矣。王事多難，維其棘矣。", "text_normalized": "我出我車，于彼牧矣。自天子所，謂我來矣。\n召彼僕夫，謂之載矣。王事多難，維其棘矣。", "notes": "出車 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-008__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-008", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·008.2", "text_original": "我出我車，于彼郊矣。設此旐矣，建彼旄矣。\n彼旟旐斯，胡不斾斾？憂心悄悄，僕夫況瘁。", "text_normalized": "我出我車，于彼郊矣。設此旐矣，建彼旄矣。\n彼旟旐斯，胡不斾斾？憂心悄悄，僕夫況瘁。", "notes": "出車 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-008__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-008", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·008.3", "text_original": "王命南仲，往城于方。出車彭彭，旂旐央央。\n天子命我，城彼朔方。赫赫南仲，玁狁于襄。", "text_normalized": "王命南仲，往城于方。出車彭彭，旂旐央央。\n天子命我，城彼朔方。赫赫南仲，玁狁于襄。", "notes": "出車 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-008__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-008", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·008.4", "text_original": "昔我往矣，黍稷方華。今我來思，雨雪載塗。\n王事多難，不遑啟居。豈不懷歸？畏此簡書。", "text_normalized": "昔我往矣，黍稷方華。今我來思，雨雪載塗。\n王事多難，不遑啟居。豈不懷歸？畏此簡書。", "notes": "出車 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-008__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-008", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·008.5", "text_original": "喓喓草蟲，趯趯阜螽。未見君子，憂心忡忡。\n既見君子，我心則降。赫赫南仲，薄伐西戎。", "text_normalized": "喓喓草蟲，趯趯阜螽。未見君子，憂心忡忡。\n既見君子，我心則降。赫赫南仲，薄伐西戎。", "notes": "出車 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-008__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-008", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·008.6", "text_original": "春日遲遲，卉木萋萋。倉庚喈喈，采蘩祁祁。\n執訊獲醜，薄言還歸。赫赫南仲，玁狁于夷。", "text_normalized": "春日遲遲，卉木萋萋。倉庚喈喈，采蘩祁祁。\n執訊獲醜，薄言還歸。赫赫南仲，玁狁于夷。", "notes": "出車 Chinese stanza 6."}
